relation: Oh, we'll get you! As soon as we navigate through your fortress and fight the eight Sanctuary Masters all over again, we'll get youuuu! You wiggle your eyebrows in vain!
When it shoots a spray of water at you, you know it's going to hurt; it doesn't matter how old it might be!
Perfect for when you're low on cash. Saturn cash, mind you.
Use it wisely, my son. This has the power to shoot stars at your enemies, correct, but it also grants wishes. You understand the stakes, yes?
